#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:0.5"
msgid "43. Sabhojanasikkhāpada"
msgstr "The training rule on lustful"

#. HTML: </h1></div><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Origin story"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc1, pts-cs-bu-pc43.1, pts-vp-en.2.354, ms2V_894 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.1"
msgid "Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery."

#. VAR: sayanighare → sayanīghare (s1-3)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā upanando sakyaputto sahāyakassa gharaṃ gantvā tassa pajāpatiyā saddhiṃ sayanighare nisajjaṃ kappesi."
msgstr "At that time Venerable Upananda the Sakyan went to the house of a friend and sat down with his wife in their bedroom."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho so puriso yenāyasmā upanando sakyaputto tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "The husband approached Upananda,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.4"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ upanandaṃ sakyaputtaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr "bowed down to him, and sat down to one side."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.5"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so puriso pajāpatiṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "He then said to his wife,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.6"
msgid "“dadehāyyassa bhikkhan”ti."
msgstr "“Please get him alms.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.7"
msgid "Atha kho sā itthī āyasmato upanandassa sakyaputtassa bhikkhaṃ adāsi."
msgstr "And she did so."

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.8"
msgid "Atha kho so puriso āyasmantaṃ upanandaṃ sakyaputtaṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "Soon afterwards he said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.9"
msgid "“gacchatha, bhante, yato ayyassa bhikkhā dinnā”ti."
msgstr "“Please leave, Venerable; the alms have been given.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.10"
msgid "Atha kho sā itthī sallakkhetvā—“pariyuṭṭhito ayaṃ puriso”ti, āyasmantaṃ upanandaṃ sakyaputtaṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "But the woman, knowing that her husband was lustful, said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.11"
msgid "“nisīdatha, bhante, mā agamitthā”ti."
msgstr "“Please sit, Venerable; don’t go.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.12"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho so puriso … pe …"
msgstr "A second time and"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.13"
msgid "tatiyampi kho so puriso āyasmantaṃ upanandaṃ sakyaputtaṃ etadavoca—“gacchatha, bhante, yato ayyassa bhikkhā dinnā”ti."
msgstr "a third time he repeated his request,"

#. REF: pts-vp-en.2.355, ms2V_895 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.14"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho sā itthī āyasmantaṃ upanandaṃ sakyaputtaṃ etadavoca—“nisīdatha, bhante, mā agamitthā”ti."
msgstr "and both times his wife repeated hers."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.15"
msgid "Atha kho so puriso nikkhamitvā bhikkhū ujjhāpesi—"
msgstr "He then left the house and complained to the other monks,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.16"
msgid "“ayaṃ, bhante, ayyo upanando mayhaṃ pajāpatiyā saddhiṃ sayanighare nisinno."
msgstr "“Venerables, Venerable Upananda is seated with my wife in our bedroom."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.17"
msgid "So mayā uyyojīyamāno na icchati gantuṃ."
msgstr "When I ask him to leave, he doesn’t want to go."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.18"
msgid "Bahukiccā mayaṃ bahukaraṇīyā”ti."
msgstr "Yet we are very busy.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3, pts-vp-pli4.95, ms2V_896 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.19"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "The monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.20"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized Upananda,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.21"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma āyasmā upanando sakyaputto sabhojane kule anupakhajja nisajjaṃ kappessatī”ti … pe …"
msgstr "“How can Venerable Upananda  sit down intruding on a lustful couple?” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.22"
msgid "“saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, upananda, sabhojane kule anupakhajja nisajjaṃ kappesī”ti?"
msgstr "“Is it true, Upananda, that you did this?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.23"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.24"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked him, “…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.25"
msgid "kathañhi nāma tvaṃ, moghapurisa, sabhojane kule anupakhajja nisajjaṃ kappessasi."
msgstr "Foolish man, how can you sit down intruding on a lustful couple?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.26"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisa, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.27"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:"

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.27a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Final ruling"

#. HTML: </h2><p><span class="rule">
#. REF: sc4, ms2V_897
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:1.28"
msgid "“Yo pana bhikkhu sabhojane kule anupakhajja nisajjaṃ kappeyya, pācittiyan”ti."
msgstr "‘If a monk sits down intruding on a lustful couple, he commits an offense entailing confession.’”"

#. HTML: </span></p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Definitions"

#. HTML: </h2><p><span class="term">
#. REF: sc5, pts-cs-bu-pc43.2.1, pts-vp-en.2.356, ms2V_898
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.1.1"
msgid "Yo panāti"
msgstr "A:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.1.2"
msgid "yo yādiso … pe …"
msgstr "whoever …"

#. HTML: </span><span class="term">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.1.3"
msgid "bhikkhūti"
msgstr "Monk:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.1.4"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr "… The monk who has been given the full ordination by a complete Order through a procedure consisting of one motion and three announcements that is unchallengeable and fit to stand—"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.1.5"
msgid "ayaṃ imasmiṃ atthe adhippeto bhikkhūti."
msgstr "this sort of monk is meant in this case."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term">
#. REF: sc6, ms2V_899
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.1.6"
msgid "Sabhojanaṃ nāma"
msgstr "A lustful couple:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.1.7"
msgid "kulaṃ itthī ceva hoti puriso ca, itthī ca puriso ca ubho anikkhantā honti, ubho avītarāgā."
msgstr "there is both a woman and a man. The woman and the man have not both left, and both are not without sensual desire."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term">
#. REF: sc7, ms2V_900
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.1.8"
msgid "Anupakhajjāti"
msgstr "Intruding on:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.1.9"
msgid "anupavisitvā."
msgstr "enters after."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term">
#. REF: sc8, ms2V_901
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.1.10"
msgid "Nisajjaṃ kappeyyāti"
msgstr "Sits down:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss">
#. VAR: piṭṭhasaṅghāṭassa → piṭṭhi­saṅghā­ṭassa (s2, s3) | piṭṭha­saṅghā­tassa (pts1) | pīṭha­saṅghā­ṭassa (itipi)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.1.11"
msgid "mahallake ghare piṭṭhasaṅghāṭassa hatthapāsaṃ vijahitvā nisīdati, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "in a large house, if he sits down more than one arm’s reach beyond the door frame, he commits an offense entailing confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.1.12"
msgid "Khuddake ghare piṭṭhivaṃsaṃ atikkamitvā nisīdati, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "In a small house, if he sits down after going beyond the ridge beam, he commits an offense entailing confession."

#. HTML: </span></p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.2.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Permutations"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc9, pts-cs-bu-pc43.2.2, ms2V_902 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.2.1"
msgid "Sayanighare sayanigharasaññī sabhojane kule anupakhajja nisajjaṃ kappeti, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "If it is a bedroom, and he perceives it as a bedroom, and he sits down intruding on a lustful couple, he commits an offense entailing confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.2.2"
msgid "Sayanighare vematiko sabhojane kule anupakhajja nisajjaṃ kappeti, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "If it is a bedroom, but he is unsure if it is, and he sits down intruding on a lustful couple, he commits an offense entailing confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.2.3"
msgid "Sayanighare nasayanigharasaññī sabhojane kule anupakhajja nisajjaṃ kappeti, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "If it is a bedroom, but he does not perceive it as a bedroom, and he sits down intruding on a lustful couple, he commits an offense entailing confession."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10, ms2V_903 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.2.4"
msgid "Nasayanighare sayanigharasaññī, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If it is not a bedroom, but he perceives it as a bedroom, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.2.5"
msgid "Nasayanighare vematiko, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If it is not a bedroom, but he is unsure of it, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.2.6"
msgid "Nasayanighare nasayanigharasaññī, anāpatti."
msgstr "If it is not a bedroom, and he does not perceives it as a bedroom, there is no offense."

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.3.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc11, pts-cs-bu-pc43.2.3, ms2V_904 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.3.1"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.3.2"
msgid "mahallake ghare piṭṭhasaṅghāṭassa hatthapāsaṃ avijahitvā nisīdati,      "
msgstr "if, in a large house, he sits down, but not beyond one arm’s reach of the door frame;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.3.3"
msgid "khuddake ghare piṭṭhivaṃsaṃ anatikkamitvā nisīdati,"
msgstr "if, in a small house, he sits down, but not beyond the ridge beam;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.3.4"
msgid "bhikkhu dutiyo hoti,"
msgstr "if he has a monk as a companion;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.3.5"
msgid "ubho nikkhantā honti,"
msgstr "if both have left;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.3.6"
msgid "ubho vītarāgā,"
msgstr "if both are without sensual desire;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.3.7"
msgid "nasayanighare,"
msgstr "if it is not a bedroom;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.3.8"
msgid "ummattakassa,"
msgstr "if he is insane;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.3.9"
msgid "ādikammikassāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. HTML: </p><hr><p class="endsutta">
#. REF: sc12, ms2V_905 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc43:2.3.10"
msgid "Sabhojanasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ tatiyaṃ."
msgstr "The third rule, the training rule on lustful, is finished."
